         Joined by ops leads, founders, and automation engineers. Weekly, no spam.
       </p>
     </div>

     <div class="lg:col-span-8 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-8">
       {columns.map((col) => (
         <div>
           <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] font-medium text-white/50 mb-4">{col.title}</p>
           <ul class="space-y-2.5">
